---
description:
Accessibility standards for LexMastery.

alwaysApply: true
---

# Accessibility

Accessibility is mandatory.

Not optional.

---

# Standards

Target WCAG 2.2 AA.

---

# Touch Targets

Minimum

48dp

---

# Contrast

Meet accessibility contrast requirements.

Never rely on color alone.

---

# Screen Readers

Provide semantic labels.

Describe icons.

Announce important changes.

---

# Typography

Support dynamic text scaling.

Never clip text.

---

# Focus

Keyboard navigation must remain logical.

Visible focus indicators required.

---

# Motion

Respect reduced motion settings.

---

# Cursor Instructions

Every generated screen should pass an accessibility review.